+The `no-wildcard-imports` rule forbids wildcard imports, except for imports defined in `.editorconfig` property `ij_kotlin_packages_to_use_import_on_demand`. If this property is not explicitly set, it allows wildcard imports like `java.util.*` by default for all codestyles except `ktlint_official` to keep in sync with IntelliJ IDEA behavior.
